 :commentary "\
Hide/show comments in code.


 Macros defined here:

   `with-comments-hidden'.

 Commands defined here:

   `hide/show-comments',

 User options defined here:

   `ignore-comments-flag'.


 Put this in your init file (`~/.emacs'):

  (require 'hide-comnt)")
